<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476000' id='t-476000'>And what I did for the first war, after we have lost everything,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='482000' id='t-482000'>I have to save something, even myself, my life and life of the staff.</span>
