<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='499000' id='t-499000'>on the canopy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='501000' id='t-501000'>And with the material that's left --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='503000' id='t-503000'>because they wanted to destroy it, to burn it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='506000' id='t-506000'>they didn't understand it, they didn't go to school --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='508000' id='t-508000'>I packed it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='510000' id='t-510000'>And that is me, going to, hurrying to Uganda,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='514000' id='t-514000'>to try to save that 4,000 material,</span>
