<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:57
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='646000' id='t-646000'>But I was doing that, negotiating with them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='649000' id='t-649000'>Sometimes we are having meeting</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='651000' id='t-651000'>and they are talking with Jean-Pierre Bemba,</span>
