<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='657000' id='t-657000'>Sometimes, they talk to my own language, that is, Lingala.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='660000' id='t-660000'>I hear it and what strategy they are doing, what they are planning.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='664000' id='t-664000'>Sometimes, they are having a helicopter</span>
