<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='668000' id='t-668000'>They used me to carry that, and I was doing counting,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='673000' id='t-673000'>what comes from where, and where, and where.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='675000' id='t-675000'>I had only this equipment -- my satellite phone, my computer</span>
