<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695000' id='t-695000'>I go, I write a short email, send it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698000' id='t-698000'>I don't know how many people I had on my address.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702000' id='t-702000'>I sent the message: what is going about the progress of the war</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='706000' id='t-706000'>and what they are planning to do.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='708000' id='t-708000'>They started suspecting that what we do on the morning,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='712000' id='t-712000'>and the afternoon, it's on the news, BBC, RFI.</span>
