<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='716000' id='t-716000'>Something might be going on.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='718000' id='t-718000'>And one day, we went for a meeting.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='720000' id='t-720000'>(Applause)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722000' id='t-722000'>Sorry.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:17
