<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='726000' id='t-726000'>One day, we went to meet the Chief Commander.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='728000' id='t-728000'>He had the same iridium cell phone like me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='731000' id='t-731000'>And he asked me, &quot;Do you know how to use this?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='733000' id='t-733000'>I said, &quot;I have never seen it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='735000' id='t-735000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='736000' id='t-736000'>I don't know.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='738000' id='t-738000'>And I had mine on my pocket.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='740000' id='t-740000'>So, it was a chance that they trusted me a lot.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='742000' id='t-742000'>They didn't -- they was not looking on me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='744000' id='t-744000'>So I was scared.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='746000' id='t-746000'>And when we finished the meeting, I went to return it in the forest.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='750000' id='t-750000'>And I was sending news, doing whatever,</span>
