<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='759000' id='t-759000'>what have been going.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='761000' id='t-761000'>And for that, they have been having big pressure to leave, to free the area.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='766000' id='t-766000'>Because there was no way --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='768000' id='t-768000'>whatever they do, it's known the same time.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:01
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='770000' id='t-770000'>During the first two rebellions, they killed all animals in the zoo.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='775000' id='t-775000'>We have a zoo of 14 Okapis, and one of them was pregnant.</span>
