<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='822000' id='t-822000'>And I succeeded.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='824000' id='t-824000'>The elephant just decayed and they just got the tusks.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:00
</data>
