<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='829000' id='t-829000'>What we are doing after that -- that was the situation of the war --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='834000' id='t-834000'>we have to rebuild.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='836000' id='t-836000'>I had some money. I was paid 150 dollars.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='839000' id='t-839000'>I devoted half of it to rebuild the herbarium,</span>
