<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='874000' id='t-874000'>And also, what one of the speciality we are doing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='877000' id='t-877000'>my design is tracking the global warming effect on biodiversity,</span>
