<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='961000' id='t-961000'>Now we say, oh, my God.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='962000' id='t-962000'>See what the wars in Rwanda.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='964000' id='t-964000'>That's because of the language of guns.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='968000' id='t-968000'>I don't think that someone may blame Google,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='972000' id='t-972000'>because it's doing the right things,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='975000' id='t-975000'>even if people like Al-Qaeda are using Google</span>
