<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='980000' id='t-980000'>But it's serving millions for the best.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='983000' id='t-983000'>But what is doing with gun industries?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='986000' id='t-986000'>Thank you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='988000' id='t-988000'>(Applause)</span>
