<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='993000' id='t-993000'>Chris Anderson: Thank you, thank you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='995000' id='t-995000'>Just wait over there.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='998000' id='t-998000'>It's an amazing story.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1000000' id='t-1000000'>I suspect a lot of people here have the same question I have.</span>
