<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1014000' id='t-1014000'>I think that now I feel nervous.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1016000' id='t-1016000'>And I think, helping us, people are acting sometimes by ignorance.</span>
